OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Liberty Steel has put 440 jobs at risk 
OL,6, under plans to mothball three factories
OL,7, and cut production at another.         
OL,9,FThe company announced plants in West   
OL,10,FBromwich, Newport and Tredegar would be
OL,11,Fmade idle as part of a restructuring of
OL,12,Fits business.                          
OL,14,FMeanwhile, production at Rotherham will
OL,15,Fbe scaled back due to high energy costs
OL,16,Fand foreign imports, which Liberty said
OL,17,Fhad made its operations "unviable".    
OL,19,FA union described the announcement as a
OL,20,F"body blow" to workers.                
